            <p class=" abt-delhi mb-20">
                Delhi is love, Delhi is haste, Delhi is serene, Delhi is chaos - It is the yang to its own yin. Delhi is a complete deal!
                From the bustling lanes of Chandni Chowk to the serene and tranquil abode of Bangla Sahib,
                Delhi makes a complete circle of life.

